@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram

autonumber
autoactivate on

Actor "Client" as client
participant "UI" as ui
participant "restDB" as restdb

note over client, restdb: The user goes to the Settings screen and presses the "EXPORT DATA" button

client -> ui: Presses the "EXPORT DATA" button
    ui -> restdb: Requests user's information
    restdb --> ui: User's information
    ui -> restdb: Requests user's leaderboard information
    restdb --> ui: User's leaderboard information
    ui -> ui: Write all retrieved data in a JSON file
    ui --> ui
ui --> client: Open intent to share the generated file
@enduml